%% State — User Account
stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> active: register()<br/>(isActive=true, role=customer)

  active --> locked: Admin set isActive=false<br/>(vd: vi phạm)
  locked --> active: Admin mở khóa

  active --> promoted: Admin gán role=admin
  promoted --> active: Admin gỡ quyền admin

  active --> deleted: Admin xóa<br/>(không còn booking active)
  locked --> deleted: Admin xóa

  deleted --> [*]

  note right of locked
    Login bị chặn:
    res.status(403)
    "Tài khoản đã bị khóa"
  end note
